data.title: "The Angry Video Game Nerd" The Rocketeer (NES & SNES) (TV Episode 2021)
data.meta_description: The Rocketeer (NES & SNES): Directed by James Rolfe. With James Rolfe. The Rocketeer was a decent comic series, but made for a forgettable movie. Though like most properties, it got video game tie-ins, which the Nerd wishes were forgotten too.
data.text:
The Angry Video Game Nerd: In short, The Rocketeer might be better than lots of the games I've reviewed for the NES, but that's actually a sad thing to say. All these years, I'm coming to realize the NES has less games like Contra and more like The Rocketeer, and when you wanna add up all the really bad ones, it's a pretty shitty library. You know what? I can't believe I'm saying this, but the NES sucked.

The Angry Video Game Nerd: I wanna be the Rocketeer, not Cliff in a plane. I wanna be the Rocketeer!

[cuts to the Rocketeer now playable in the plane racing stage]

The Angry Video Game Nerd: The game just mocked me.
